Name: airobots
Version: 1.0.0b0
Summary: UI Test Automation Framework for Games and Apps on Android/iOS/Windows/Linux/Web
Home-page: https://github.com/BSTester/Airobots
Author: 贝克街的捉虫师
Author-email: forpeng@foxmail.com
